{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778468364664,"sessionID":"ses_1eb09b109ffeoer5llC2d0y8Fw","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"functions.bash:26","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"git add src/ontology/go-edit.obo && git commit -m \"Add part_of relationship to clathrin coat disassembly\n\nAdded relationship: part_of GO:0072583 (clathrin-dependent endocytosis) to\nGO:0072318 (clathrin coat disassembly), as suggested in issue #31981.\n\nPer discussion on the issue (pgaudet), this is correctly modeled as part_of\nrather than is_a, because clathrin coat disassembly is a step in the broader\nclathrin-dependent endocytosis process rather than a subtype of it.\n\nAlso added term_tracker_item property linking back to issue #31981.\n\nFixes #31981\"","description":"Commit changes to go-edit.obo"},"output":"[scribe-v1-ai4curation-go-ontology-agent-config-v9-.-togetherai-moonshotai-Kimi-K2.6-iter1-issue-31981 dee0244] Add part_of relationship to clathrin coat disassembly\n 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)\n","metadata":{"output":"[scribe-v1-ai4curation-go-ontology-agent-config-v9-.-togetherai-moonshotai-Kimi-K2.6-iter1-issue-31981 dee0244] Add part_of relationship to clathrin coat disassembly\n 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)\n","exit":0,"description":"Commit changes to go-edit.obo","truncated":false},"title":"Commit changes to go-edit.obo","time":{"start":1778468364660,"end":1778468364663}},"id":"prt_e14f99c4b001LQtRdsB5242m1A","sessionID":"ses_1eb09b109ffeoer5llC2d0y8Fw","messageID":"msg_e14f997f300190ytx7yJOhmbxq"}}
